flowchart TD
    A["Attack Occurs<br/>Player or Enemy"] --> B["Physics Check<br/>Overlap / Raycast / Collider"]

    B --> X{"Attack Handling Mode?"}

    X -->|"Instant attack (punch, projectile, etc.)"| C["Build HitData"]
    C --> D["HitDispatcher.ProcessHit(HitData)"]

    X -->|"Tagged attack (Fire, poison, etc.)"| T["HitDispatcher.ProcessHit(AttackDefinition)"]
    T --> D

    D --> E["Get IHitResponders<br/>from Target"]
    E --> F["Sort Responders<br/>by HitPriority"]
    F --> G["Call responder.OnHit(HitData)"]
    G --> H["Responder Returns HitResponse"]
    H --> I["HitResult.Merge(HitResponse)"]
    I -->|If Not Stopped| G
    I -->|PropagationStopped| J["Return HitResult"]
    J --> K["Attacker Reacts<br/>VFX / SFX / Future Combo"]